330
00:32:45,470 --> 00:32:49,640
I think that this must be a way to cherish
the memory of the ancient deity, Farmer God.

331
00:32:49,640 --> 00:32:52,100
He tested hundreds of herbs and took in
hundreds of poisons for the Fight Qi Continent.

332
00:32:52,100 --> 00:32:54,820
His heroic act established our alchemy industry.

